-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party conversion engine
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Universal Media Converter orchestrates FFmpeg for media conversion. FFmpeg is a
separate project and keeps its own license terms. The project may use a system
FFmpeg executable, a user-provided FFmpeg executable, or an FFmpeg binary
provided through imageio-ffmpeg.

  FFmpeg
    License: LGPL v2.1 or later for most builds; some builds include GPL
    components depending on compile-time options.
    Source:  https://ffmpeg.org/
    Legal:   https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html

