Distribution note
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This repository does not intentionally commit FFmpeg binaries. If a release
artifact bundles FFmpeg or redistributes imageio-ffmpeg-provided binaries, keep
the corresponding third-party license notices with that artifact.
